queryParams.name: metas
queryParams.description:
Metas to filter. Each entry must have the field `type` (with value `"number"`, `"multipleValues"` or `"oneValue"`). For number, use fields `value.min` and `value.max`. Else, use `value` as an array of possible meta value id, and the field `boolOperation` with `"union"` or `"intersection"`
